53.9	Voicemail	Voice-mail	There are many microprocessors throughout the system since the system must handle large amounts of data and it's unacceptable to have any wait times (for example, when the system is recording or playing your message, it's unacceptable if the system stops recording momentarily like computers often do while accessing large files).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/8/8a/Voice_Mail_Block_Diagram.jpg/600px-Voice_Mail_Block_Diagram.jpg
